snippet.title: Project N3T Trailer
snippet.description:
Take control of a test subject tasked with testing out a new device that functions as a powerful magnet. Complete a few tests by moving metal objects and using the magnet as a grappling hook in this short single-player experience.

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2594490/Project_N3T/
